The interviews were organized with semistructured questions about the relationship between actors in the supply chain (see Fig. 1 and Table 1
                     ), the mapping of wastes (Table 2
                     ), and SDG 12 global targets (Table 3
                     ). The nonparticipant observations were made with face-to-face visits to the company to validate the responses collected in the in-depth interviews. The document analysis consists of the study of information from the corporate poultry processor website, which lists reports from the institutions ABPA (2018), CRMV, 2017, and Fundesa (2014).
